nodes.text: This Unidentified individual was a Human who served aboard the Imperial-class Star Destroyer Mauler.

In 7 ABY, Warlord Zsinj launched an attack on the planet Kuat in his attempt to steal the newly constructed Executor-class Star Dreadnought Razor's Kiss. This unidentified individual assisted the operation by coordinating efforts between the boarding party on Razor's Kiss.
